title: Hour 1 - The Divisional Round begins!
itunes:title: Hour 1 - The Divisional Round begins!
description:
Dan Patrick talks about the first day of the MLB Divisional Round playoffs, the various comebacks and close games we saw yesterday, and what the next few days will bring.
